message:
Confirm object synset assignment.
Object assigned to synset: bulletin_board_system.n.01
Definition: a computer that is running software that allows users to leave messages and access information of general interest
Reminder: synset should match the object and not its contents.
(e.g. orange juice bottle needs to match orange_juice__bottle.n.01
and not orange_juice.n.01)

Confirm object properties:
- dustyable
Full list of iGibson abilities: burnable, cleaningTool, coldSource, cookable, dustyable, freezable, heatSource, liquid, openable, sliceable, slicer, soakable, stainable, toggleable, waterSource
Check incorrect or missing properties, especially liquid property
